window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>After fighting a troll in a back alley, I found out the supernatural was real.</b></p> <p>Then I discovered I'm a dragon shifter.</p> <p>Soon after, I learned I'm also a mage.</p> <p>Turns out this combination is incredibly rare, and now everyone wants a piece of me.</p> <p>Being a dragon, there's only one thing I want to do: gather my hoard.</p> <p>Power. Magic. Women. Riches. It's all going to be mine.</p>"; 
